<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038584" n="1"/>
<opener><lb/>Illustrimsimo et Doctissimo Viro
      <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-102552517">Petro Antonio Michelotti</rs>
                              <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
      <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Nicolaus Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice>.</rs> </opener>
      <p><lb/>Quas ad me remisisti <rs type="letter">litteras</rs><note type="comment">Dieser Brief ist nicht erhalten.</note> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089913338">fratris</rs> mei <date when="1719-11-07">heri</date> demum acce<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pi hic <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>, ubi (Deo sint grati<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>) salvus et incolumis redux
                              <lb/>factus sum <date>ultimo die pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>teriti mensis</date>. Intellexisti sine dubio
            <lb/>jam ex <rs type="letter" key="B_1719-11-03_991170515151205501">litteris</rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patrui</rs> mei, <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">fasciculum</rs> Tuum tandem <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basileam</rs> 
                              <lb/>venisse, doleo quod tam<del> longum</del> diu in itinere fuerit, culpa <add>ut suspicor</add> eorum
            <lb/>qui <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3173435">Mediolani</rs> negotium non recte curaverunt mittendo fasci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>culum non per Postam (ut dicunt) sed inter merces alicujus
      <lb/>mercatoris. <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruus</rs> qui plurimam salutem Tibi impertitur,
                              <pb facs="1038585" n="2"/>
            <lb/>mihi affirmavit se quam<subst><del>ntum per</del><add>primum <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice></add></subst> negoti<subst><del>a</del><add>is</add></subst> gravissim<subst><del>a</del><add>is</add></subst><del> quibus</del>
            <lb/><del>nunc obruitur, licebit </del>minus impedietur <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">dissertationem</rs> Tuam
                              <lb/>diligenter perlecturum esse;<del>eam tamen quoque, ut petis, porro cur</del>
                              <lb/>non est cur eam mihi denuo co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endes, habes enim me ad omnia
      <lb/>servitia sponte paratissimum. Adgnatus meus <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Nicolaus</rs> nunc
            <lb/><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2925177">Friburgi</rs> degit apud Generalem et Comitem <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1012270238">Harsch</rs> ejusdem
      <lb/>Fortalitii Gubernatorem. Rogo ut honoris cultum <add>meo nomine</add> deferas
                              <lb/>Fautoribus et Amicis, et excuses brevitatem epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, quam
                              <lb/>longiorem esse veta<subst><del>nt plurima impedimenta et re</del><add>t</add></subst> temporis
                              <lb/>quod mihi suppetit penuria.</p> <closer><salute>Vale et me amare perge.</salute>
                                    <dateline><lb/>Dabam <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <date when="1719-11-08"><choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>a dato</expan></choice> 8. Nov. 1719.</date></dateline></closer>
</div>
